582
00:38:28,700 --> 00:38:29,700
All right.

583
00:38:29,710 --> 00:38:30,990
You can address him how you want.

584
00:38:31,500 --> 00:38:33,180
With me around,

585
00:38:33,310 --> 00:38:34,700
you won't be taken advantage of.

586
00:38:35,000 --> 00:38:35,860
I can guarantee that.

587
