to transform into a human?)

589
00:38:48,510 --> 00:38:50,790
(When a soul beast reaches
100,000 years of cultivation,)

590
00:38:51,140 --> 00:38:52,500
(it faces two choices.)

591
00:38:53,010 --> 00:38:54,750
(One is to endure
the heavenly tribulation.)

592
00:38:55,660 --> 00:38:57,350
(If it fails, it dies.)

593
00:38:58,020 --> 00:38:58,910
(If it survives,)

594
00:38:59,350 --> 00:39:00,500
