595
00:39:00,660 --> 00:39:03,020
(another long 100,000 years)

596
00:39:03,220 --> 00:39:04,830
(and the next tribulation.)

597
00:39:05,310 --> 00:39:08,100
(The other option is
to transform into a human.)

598
00:39:08,870 --> 00:39:09,660
(Just like Wu?)

599
00:39:10,870 --> 00:39:13,270
(Won't every soul beast choose
this path?)

600
00:39:13,340 --> 00:39:15,620
