that a Hectomillennium Soul Beast)

601
00:39:15,620 --> 00:39:17,620
(is equivalent to a Titled Douluo
in human terms.)

602
00:39:18,630 --> 00:39:20,590
(But once a soul beast transforms
into a human,)

603
00:39:20,600 --> 00:39:21,890
(its cultivation resets to zero.)

604
00:39:22,140 --> 00:39:23,790
(They have to start from the beginning.)

605
00:39:24,020 --> 00:39:26,060
